00:13:44.804 --> 00:13:48.704
trimethyl compared to the one in the melanocytic cells.

232
00:13:48.804 --> 00:13:52.324
And this is even more, I think, apparent if we look at

233
00:13:52.404 --> 00:13:56.224
the western blot where the levels of this histone mark are

234
00:13:56.244 --> 00:13:59.144
extremely low in the mesenchymal cells.

235
00:14:01.024 --> 00:14:04.834
Then we subjected the melanocytic and mesenchymal cell

236
00:14:04.864 --> 00:14:08.784
lines to passage through these very narrow pores, three

237
00:14:08.864 --> 00:14:12.804
microns, trying to mimic what happens during constriction when the

238
00:14:12.944 --> 00:14:15.804
cells go through the endothelial cells and

239
00:14:16.104 --> 00:14:19.004
intravasate. And we examine the cells

240
00:14:19.124 --> 00:14:22.534
pre-invasion, pre-constriction, and

241
00:14:22.624 --> 00:14:26.504
post-migration by different omics platforms like

